nstall GitHub Copilot in the CLI, you must have an active GitHub Copilot subscription, have GitHub CLI installed, and authenticate using the GitHub CLI OAuth app. Install Copilot CLI with npm install -g @github/copilot to get started.\\n\\n### Basic Commands\\n\\nYou can ask Copilot in the CLI to suggest a command for your use case with gh copilot suggest, or to explain a command you're curious about with gh copilot explain.\\n\\n### Availability\\n\\nThe tool is included in Copilot Free, Pro, Pro+, Business, and Enterprise subscriptions.\\n\\n\\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks.\"}]},\"uuid\":\"0eb8c63c-4116-4eab-8bd4-2f6b0e714cc9\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-02T01:13:06.549Z\"},\"normalizedMessages\":[],\"type\":\"agent_progress\",\"prompt\":\"\",\"agentId\":\"a380b634d2c4dfbaf\"},\"toolUseID\":\"agent_msg_01638cr2BVFvq7kC5BYM3NZt\",\"parentToolUseID\":\"toolu_01YVXe4Pjsqg6LdHhSANNNGd\",\"uuid\":\"16b28985-a8a2-41b5-bf7d-fb4089cc1571\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-02T01:13:06.554Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"16b28985-a8a2-41b5-bf7d-fb4089cc1571\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alex/workspace/cli/.worktrees/3\",\"sessionId\":\"2335990a-d6c5-4425-96b8-9c47a378a3bd\",\"version\":\"2.1.63\",\"gitBranch\":\"alex/add-copilot-agent\",\"slug\":\"buzzing-tinkering-coral\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"message\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_01PXVDzdTbP8uUDdin7SphQa\",\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"Web search results for query: \\\"GitHub Copilot CLI terminal agent 2025 2026\\\"\\n\\nLinks: [{\\\"title\\\":\\\"GitHub Copilot CLI is now generally available - GitHub Changelog\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://github.blog/changelog/2026-02-25-github-copilot-cli-is-now-generally-available/\\\"},{\\\"title\\\":\\\"GitHub Copilot CLI · GitHub\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/features/copilot/cli\\\"},{\\\"title\\\":\\\"GitHub